  "texts": [
    "A project that is finished on time is less likely to incur additional expenses due to delays, as it ensures critical deadline are met.",
    "Cost is another frequently employed performance metric in MS-RCPSP for several reasons.",
    "It is indeed inextricably linked to the overall financial performance of the project as well as the project's budget.",
    "In many projects, cost is a key indicator of the project's efficiency, and it is frequently used as a benchmark for evaluating the effectiveness of various project scheduling strategies.",
    "One can cite for instance the works of [9,12,13]."
  ]
}